The paper deals with optimization problems related to signal processing and resource allocation in Cloud-RAN, which are typical topics in the fields of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also proposes a novel algorithm based on majorization-minimization and semidefinite relaxation techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning and optimization (cs.MM) and optimization and control (cs.LG).
